<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>قَفْزة <span class="c4">[مفرد]</span>: ج قَفَزات وقَفْزات:<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
